Timi and Busola Dakolo Timi Dakolo has spoken up following the rape allegation against COZA pastor, Biodun Fatoyinbo by the singer’s wife Busola Dakolo. In photo he shared on Instagram, Timi talked about a child finding her voice and letting go of the fear of people seeing her in a negative way. He captioned the photo: ‘The Little Girl Didn’t Die.’ Read below:    The post “The Little Girl Didn’t Die” – Timi Dakolo speaks after Wife Busola’s Rape Allegation Against Pastor Biodun Fatoyinbo appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija